org.afplib.afplib

Interface TileTOCRG

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TileTOCRGImpl

    public interface TileTOCRG
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'Tile TOCRG'.

    The following features are supported:

    • XOFFSET
    • YOFFSET
    • THSIZE
    • TVSIZE
    • RELRES
    • COMPR
    • DATAPOS

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getTileTOCRG()
